name: Rush Ceramic Speed Bombers
description:
RUSH, your new favorite longboard bearing. The fastest bearing of the Rush line, this is the best all-weather option for the serious longboarder. These Bearings have an innovative stability locking system in the spacers for an extra smooth ride when bombing hills and catching major speed. Black ceramic ball bearings, stainless steel casing. Extra fast, strong and long lasting. 
8 pack.
4 Spacers and Bearing Lube also included.

name: Perfecto Dos Drop-Down Racer
description: All Maple drop-down racer. Drop through trucks keeps your gravity low and increase your stability while the drop down design keeps your feet locked on the deck and gives you more comfortable control at high speeds. Great for cruising around town, cutting some tight slalom corners or catching some major, major speed, carves, and slides on your local downhill spot of choice. Construction 9 Ply Maple Length: 39.75" Width: 9.75" Drop Through Mounting Drop Down camber Concave: Medium Components -71 mm x 51mm 80a clear yellow wheels -7" aluminum reverse kingpin Camino truck -RUSH ABEC 5 bearings -Black Hardware -Black grip tape

name: "Everything Drains" Save Japan Dolphins
description: Bring out your inner activist and join us in our ocean awareness campaign with the "Everything Drains" bamboo core Racing series.
